sentences: Barrière worked at the Service de la Recherche, ORTF, and in 1970 became co-founder and director of the International Institute of Electroacoustic Music of Bourges with Christian Clozier.
Barrière was a founder of the International Confederation of Electroacoustic Music (ICEM) and served as its president beginning in 2005.
Barriere died in 2019 at the age of 76.
